{"tid":1586822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔需要申請不反對通知既活動","createTime":"2019-09-22T06:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:45:11.000Z","uid":290407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a238d0d825c24b37a9387a24ef28ed44a006a626","tid":1586822,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>商場唱歌、人鏈，已經有左共識係唔會申請不反對通知，不過係限制於某個區，人數有限。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不如大家諗下，有咩活動可以動員全港人，又可以擺到明唔申請不反對通知呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">粗人鏈</span>有冇得諗? 唔霸路，但塞滿行人路，係一般人鏈5倍咁粗。主打銅鑼灣至中環。基本上係遊行但唔郁亦唔行馬路。<br />\n<br />\n或者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民行山</span>! 搵條容易行既行山徑，3個鐘內行完!<br />\n<br />\n一定要200%和理非!<br />\n<br />\n而家警方唔批民陣活動，我地要諗計突圍，唔可以俾警察食住上。"},{"pid":"9420b1129561e731691c11d85aa6e9e6b4c8f433","tid":1586822,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【和你shop攻略】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581869\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581869</a></span><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"20bb8f35ddfd6047d59320c1c06cca6681c42d07","tid":1586822,"uid":290407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"其實何妖俾左個提示香港人: 有些活動係唔需要申請不反對通知既...."},{"pid":"27638794029698f594da16e21160b43ab16b932c","tid":1586822,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee59924c02815849b5ab7e7029da5a98c797b75e","tid":1586822,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20bb8f35ddfd6047d59320c1c06cca6681c42d07","tid":1586822,"uid":290407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"其實何妖俾左個提示香港人: 有些活動係唔需要申請不反對通知既...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"。。。係因為撐警啫"},{"pid":"d223787b95a4c9e89d07070ddb2bf91